        {
            "title": "英格蘭國家隊｜杜曹:福仔是時候重返三獅軍 拉舒福特8字回應",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"杜曹指福仔是時候重返三獅軍，拉舒福特8字回應。REUTERS\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/b60844d441196834bb7045c4866f10ec/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250315/_2025031509561194228.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">杜曹指福仔是時候重返三獅軍，拉舒福特8字回應。REUTERS</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>拉舒福特於冬季轉會市場由曼聯外借到阿士東維拉後如獲重生，表現獲維拉主帥艾馬利讚賞，並成功入選英格蘭新領隊杜曹第一次公布的三獅大軍名單。杜曹指拉舒福特是時候返回三獅軍，福仔以8字回應重返三獅軍的心情。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"英格蘭領隊杜曹(中)重召拉舒福特入伍。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e40462d33b294916051b32c68ab981dc/2025-03/2025-01-18T150534Z_952614961_UP1EL1I15X8SV_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-WHU-CRY-REPORT.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        英格蘭領隊杜曹(中)重召拉舒福特入伍。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"拉舒福特重返英格蘭國家隊。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ffc32bf264798728d0b1f18cd06b9564/2025-03/6_3_1_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        拉舒福特重返英格蘭國家隊。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"拉舒福特加盟維拉後表現持續勇猛。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c9182250712bc41b70394acba9b00ff7/2025-03/2025-02-28T202301Z_2094870222_UP1EL2S1KMBFX_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-AVL-CAR-REPORT_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        拉舒福特加盟維拉後表現持續勇猛。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"拉舒福特(右)加盟維拉後表現持續勇猛。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bd4f98b4e1c0432377d9f489dda62cd2/2025-03/2025-02-28T212915Z_1579538791_UP1EL2S1NOQJV_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-AVL-CAR-REPORT_1.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        拉舒福特(右)加盟維拉後表現持續勇猛。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"拉舒福特(右)很高興重返英格蘭國家隊。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7c114c2487e070160e8d8c71f3671c81/2025-03/2025-02-28T212839Z_1965519778_UP1EL2S1NNPJP_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-AVL-CAR-REPORT_1.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        拉舒福特(右)很高興重返英格蘭國家隊。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"拉舒福特很高興重返英格蘭國家隊。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/535887e5570dfde636c8054a80144363/2025-03/2025-02-28T212956Z_920227299_UP1EL2S1NPUJY_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-AVL-CAR-REPORT_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        拉舒福特很高興重返英格蘭國家隊。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"拉舒福特(右)很高興重返英格蘭國家隊。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3c6971bbfb8a530b704f482dda9e60ab/2025-03/2025-02-28T214140Z_1875920046_UP1EL2S1O9ELD_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-AVL-CAR-REPORT_1.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        拉舒福特(右)很高興重返英格蘭國家隊。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"拉舒福特(右)加盟維拉後表現持續勇猛。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/086c93c9e6bcb5f8245b7133186ab609/2025-03/2025-02-28T214018Z_1181382135_UP1EL2S1O74L8_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-AVL-CAR-REPORT_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        拉舒福特(右)加盟維拉後表現持續勇猛。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>杜曹：推動福仔保持狀態</h2>\n<p>英格蘭領隊杜曹就他徵召拉舒福特入伍作出解釋，指現在是合適的時間讓拉舒福特重返國家隊：「我感覺到拉舒福特在維拉有重大的影響力，他多次後備上陣對賽果都有極大影響。他體能的影響最令人印象深刻和最重要，他的工作效率、防守影響，他在反擊中的努力、回防時補位都令人印象深刻。我有強列的感覺要選他入伍，將他帶回國家隊推動他要保持現在於維拉的狀態，而不是返回之前的低潮。今次集訓要與他建立聯繫，並推動他保持在高水平。」\n\n</p><h2>拉舒福特：不要放棄信念</h2>\n<p>自從魯賓艾摩廉在去年11月1日接替被炒的坦哈格出任曼聯領隊之後，拉舒福特便失去正選席位，之後更因與艾摩廉不和被剔出比賽大軍名單；而他因狀態麻麻自去年3月起便沒有入選英格蘭國家隊。拉舒福特在今年一月冬季轉會市場被曼聯外借到維拉，無論訓練和場上的表現都大獲好評，至今於各項賽事為維拉9次上陣交出4次助攻，並成功打動三獅主帥杜曹選他入最新公布的大軍名單，「福仔」8字回應重返國家隊：「不要放棄信念，急不及代要開始！」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
